org.sbml.jsbml.validator.offline.constraints

Interface CoreSpecialErrorCodes

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TreeNodeConstraints

    public interface CoreSpecialErrorCodes
    Some ErrorCodes which are not officially part of SBML and only are used for offline validation. In general, there are no SBMLError objects for this codes, because they are only used for special cases.
    Since:
    1.2
